# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.2.5] - 2024-12-04


### Changed
- Publish version stable package to npm registry https://www.npmjs.com/package/@vkhangstack/veloqr/v/1.2.5
- Code example updates
- Version bump to 1.2.5

## [1.2.4] - 2024-11-25

### Changed
- Refactored image processing to post to worker
- Version bump to 1.2.4

## [1.2.3] - 2024-11-24

### Added
- WASM file caching support
- `decodeQRFromImageData` method
- Single instance camera usage

### Changed
- Version bump to 1.2.3

## [1.2.2] - 2024-11-23

### Changed
- Updated README.npm
- Version bump to 1.2.2

## [1.2.1] - 2024-11-22

### Added
- Flash/torch switch button for supported devices
- `flash` method and enum types
- Vibration support with `isVibrationSupported` method

### Fixed
- NotReadableError in Samsung Chrome browser

### Changed
- UI: Updated demo page height
- Refactored vibrate functionality
- Refactored `getCameraDevices` method
- Updated worker source

## [1.2.0] - 2024-11-20

### Added
- MRZ (Machine Readable Zone) scanning support for passports and ID cards
  - TD1 format (ID cards: 3 lines of 30 characters)
  - TD2 format (travel documents: 2 lines of 36 characters)
  - TD3 format (passports: 2 lines of 44 characters)
- `MRZScanner` component for live MRZ scanning
- `MRZImageScanner` component for image file MRZ scanning
- `useMRZScanner` hook for advanced MRZ scanning control
- MRZ utility functions: `formatMRZDate`, `validateMRZ`, `validateCheckDigit`
- OCR integration using Tesseract.js for MRZ text recognition
- Rust WASM implementation for MRZ parsing (`parse_mrz_text`)

### Changed
- Optimized QR code scanning for very small codes
- Refactored worker helper to use switch case pattern
- Auto-hide detection overlay after `detectionDuration`
- Updated version script

## [1.1.0] - 2024-11-15

### Added
- Frame merging for better accuracy
- Camera switching support with `showCameraSwitch` prop
- `preferredCamera` option (front/back or user/environment)
- Multiple camera device selection
- `getCameraDevices` utility function

### Changed
- Improved Safari compatibility
- Optimized performance for real-time scanning

## [1.0.3] - 2024-11-10

### Added
- Custom text and internationalization support
- Pre-configured language support (Vietnamese, English, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, French)
- `getTextsByLanguage` utility function
- Animation configuration options
- Custom styling props

### Changed
- Improved animation feedback
- Enhanced overlay customization

## [1.0.2] - 2024-11-08

### Fixed
- WASM loading issues in production builds
- Camera permission handling

### Changed
- Improved error messages
- Better documentation

## [1.0.1] - 2024-11-05

### Added
- Image file scanning support with `QRImageScanner`
- Multiple QR code detection in single frame

### Fixed
- Memory leaks in camera stream
- iOS Safari camera issues

## [1.0.0] - 2024-11-01

### Added
- Initial release
- Real-time QR code scanning from webcam
- `QRScanner` component
- `useQRScanner` hook
- WebAssembly-powered QR detection using Rust
- TypeScript support
- Customizable animations and overlays
